list.abstract: Territory，英文单词，译为领地，领土，版图，领域，范围， [商]势力范围。

yingyinNormal.en: It's occupied territory. He's not deploying on sovereign land. So, as Commander in Chief, he doesn't need Congressional approval.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是占领区 ，他并未向他国领土派兵。作为三军统帅，他不需要得到国会批准。

yingyinNormal.en: Captain Kirk, without authorization and in league with the fugitive John Harrison, you went rogue in enemy territory, leaving me no choice but to hunt you down and destroy you. Lock phasers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 柯克舰长，你未经授权与逃犯约翰·哈里森结盟闯入敌方领土，我别无选择，只能击杀你们。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm off to go find the Tribal Territory. Oh, goodbye!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要去找野人领地了，再见！

yingyinNormal.en: You can hide here, and hunt here. Each has its own territory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 既可隐匿于此，也可狩猎于此，一切生命都有自己的领地。

yingyinNormal.en: Every ship has one. A what? A map. What does that say? Tribal Territory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有船都有一张。什么？一张地图。上面说什么？“野人领地”。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, please, Ross it was so obvious. It was like you were marking your territory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，罗斯，这实在太明显了，你好像在划定地盘。

yingyinNormal.en: From here, I can also see the remains of a road that cuts across the Yanomami territory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在上空，我还能看到残存的横穿雅诺玛米领地的道路。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: As soon as we're clear of their territory, we can stop. You can come with me. Nothing here on out but slaughter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一旦经过了他们的领地，就能停车了，你们可以跟我一起走，这里只有杀戮。

yingyinNormal.en: We're in Ghost Nation territory. Most savage tribe there is. Those are the folks who came calling without an invitation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们已经到了幽灵之国，这里到处都是野蛮人的部落，那是些不请自来的人的头骨。

yingyinNormal.en: But a few years ago, I decided, as you will, at some point, that it was time to recalculate, find new territory, break new ground.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但在若干年前，我做出了决定，各位将来也会和我一样，会在某一时刻认为自己要重新开始，寻找新版图，开辟新天地。

yingyinNormal.en: For castaways who must share their lifeboats with large dangerous carnivores, it's advisable to establish your territory as your own.
yingyinNormal.zh: 若遇难者必须与大型肉食动物共用救生艇，建议你们划分清楚地盘。

yingyinNormal.en: That's me. Listen, you and I are gonna be sharing a bed. You know, this is uncharted territory for both of us. How are you feeling about that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，兵是我。听我说，你和我要睡在一张床上了，这件事对于我俩都是头一次，你对此有何感想？

yingyinNormal.en: Outside the urban areas, visitors are often surprised to learn that over forty percent of the Hong Kong's territory has been designated as national park.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在市区，游客会对香港有超过四成地方获指定为公园感到惊讶。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
